title: A new subdivision of Serene Hills, Las Colinas Estates, is located in the northwest quadrant of the ...

attachments.displayName:
A new subdivision of Serene Hills, Las Colinas Estates, is located in the northwest quadrant of the community. This beautiful subdivision has large home sites of up to 1.5 acres which will feature homes from $850,000 to $2,000,000, gorgeous canyon and Serene Hills Nature Preserve views!
Contact +Linda Dittoe, Austin Real Estate, Austin Here I Come for more info on this new development.
http://serene-hills.com/news
